nodes.text: Hunvicko was a subsidiary of the InterGalactic Banking Clan that went bankrupt during the Clone Wars.

Hunvicko was first mentioned under the name Huvicko in the 2003 Star Wars Legends sourcebook Coruscant and the Core Worlds. It was established to be canon by "An Old Friend," the fifth episode of the canon animated series Star Wars: The Clone Wars' sixth season.
